  <!-- Edit Modal -->
  <div class="modal fade" id="editModal" tabindex="-1"><div class="modal-dialog modal-xl"><div class="modal-content"><div class="modal-header bg-light"><h5 class="modal-title fw-bold"><i class="fas fa-edit me-2"></i>登録内容の修正</h5><button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal"></button></div><div class="modal-body p-0"><input type="hidden" id="editId"><div class="row g-0"><div class="col-lg-6 border-end bg-dark d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center p-2" style="min-height: 500px;"><iframe id="previewFrame" class="preview-frame" src=""></iframe><div id="noPreview" class="text-white text-center" style="display:none;"><i class="fas fa-eye-slash fa-3x mb-3"></i><br>プレビューできません</div></div><div class="col-lg-6 p-4" style="max-height: 80vh; overflow-y: auto;"><div class="alert alert-info py-2 small mb-3"><i class="fas fa-magic me-1"></i> AI解析結果を確認し、修正してください。</div><div class="row g-3"><div class="col-md-6"><label class="form-label fw-bold small text-muted">利用日</label><input type="date" class="form-control" id="editDate"></div><div class="col-md-6"><label class="form-label fw-bold small text-muted">支払先</label><input type="text" class="form-control" id="editStore"></div><div class="col-12"><div class="card bg-light border-0 p-3"><h6 class="fw-bold mb-3 border-bottom pb-2 small text-muted">明細情報</h6><div class="row g-2 align-items-center"><div class="col-4"><label class="small text-muted mb-1">勘定科目</label><input type="text" class="form-control form-control-sm" id="editCat" list="categoryList" placeholder="科目"></div><div class="col-4"><label class="small text-muted mb-1">品目名</label><input type="text" class="form-control form-control-sm" id="editItem" placeholder="品名"></div><div class="col-4"><label class="small text-muted mb-1">金額(税込)</label><input type="number" class="form-control form-control-sm text-end fw-bold" id="editAmount" placeholder="金額"></div></div></div></div><div class="col-12 mt-2"><div class="form-check p-3 border rounded"><input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" id="editInvoice"><label class="form-check-label" for="editInvoice">インボイス登録番号あり (T + 13桁)</label></div></div></div><div class="mt-4 d-grid gap-2"><button type="button" class="btn btn-primary fw-bold btn-lg" onclick="saveEdit()"><i class="fas fa-save me-2"></i>修正を保存する</button><button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">キャンセル</button></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>

